BREAKING: The new President of Poland, Karol Nawrocki, called on the European Union to respect the sovereignty of European nations and Christian values.

BREAKING: NEW POLISH PRESIDENT CONFRONTS EU OVER SOVEREIGNTY & VALUES President Karol Nawrocki has issued a bold call for Brussels to respect the sovereignty of European nations and uphold Christian values. “Poland will not be dictated to. We will defend our traditions and our right to self-determination.” WHAT THIS MEANS: Poland is signaling a major shift in tone toward the EU Sovereignty and identity are back at the center of European politics Nawrocki is positioning Poland as a voice for cultural conservatism and national rights A new chapter begins — and Poland is stepping forward to lead it.
